\Omega,\Omega^*
\Bbb R^n
h\in C^{2,1}(\Bbb R^n)
\Omega^*
\Omega^*=\{p\in\Bbb R^n|h(p)\gt 0\}
\|D h\|\ne 0
D h=\nabla h
Du(\Omega)=\Omega^*
h(Du)=0
\partial\Omega
H=h(Du)
H\gt 0
\Omega
H=0
\partial\Omega
D_\tau H=h_{p_k}D_{k\tau}u=0
\partial\Omega
D_\nu H=h_{p_k}D_{k\nu}u\ge 0
\partial\Omega
h_{p_k}
p=Du
